response.overview: A reporter on the trail of a sinister cult wakes up in a morgue to find herself a member of the undead. She goes on a personal vendetta for a group a cultists that are responsible for her death.
response.tagline: They didn't leave her alive. They left her UNDEAD.
response.title: Rise: Blood Hunter
